content.text: From August 22-23, 2025, the elizaOS/eliza repository showed active development with 2 new pull requests (with 1 successfully merged), 2 new issues opened, and involvement from 6 active contributors during this period.

Issue #5809 titled 'Image Generation not working in Discord' by @harperaa is OPEN with no comments since its creation on August 22, 2025.
